{"tid":1958191,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"［警世］重新出發-抗爭生活化","createTime":"2020-04-04T12:26:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-07T10:21:34.000Z","uid":329034,"like":108,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":81,"replies":[{"pid":"b20bcb36fc63ca5110de2d6ca5952054fcad6c1d","tid":1958191,"uid":329034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T12:26:41.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">*重點喺下面*</span><br />\n抗爭踏入第十一個月，眼見身邊人熱情減退、勇武手足陸續被判刑，這場逆權運動，終究要失敗收場了嗎？ <br />\n其實換個角度，運動持續了十一個月已算打破了香港歷史。 的確，勇武在運動中的影響力下降了，<br />\n但至少，我們逼使了政權撤回惡法。 <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">請謹記，用不同方法成就五大訴求，才不是把手足當Condom。</span><br />\n<br />\n因此，小弟斗膽提出己見 ，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">係時候將抗爭生活化</span></strong>。<br />\n<br />\n老實講呢句說話聽咗咁耐，究竟即係點呢？<br />\n<br />\n我認為只要每一個人每日抽少少時間出嚟，<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">做最自己最有效率嘅事</span></span>，聚沙成塔就會好有效果。<br />\n咁大家有咩崗位係大家可以參與嘅呢？<br />\n<br />\n而我認為有三大戰線值得注意 - 資訊戰、立法會選舉同經濟戰<br />\n<br />\n資訊戰  簡單來說，即是靠大家對本地文宣創作的支持，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">鼓勵手足繼續創作高質文宣。</span></span><br />\n與此同時，透過吸收更多不同嘅知識，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">去裝備好自己</span></span>，為本來嘅戰役做好準備。<br />\n<br />\n原因：<br />\n- 要保持一定人數創作文宣，繼續推動運動發展。<br />\n- 對家不斷進步緊，我地何以能夠怠慢？<br />\n<br />\n點做？<br />\n <span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">1) CLS (Comment Like Share) </span></span><br />\n- 有好文唔好收收埋埋，比身邊人一齊學嘢，一齊討論<br />\n- 每一次CLS會令文宣比更多人睇到<br />\n- 每一個like 都係文宣創作人繼續努力嘅動力<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">2) 支持原創</span></span><br />\n- 文宣也是藝術創作，尊重文宣創作人<br />\n- 良心做人，勿偷圖<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">3) 多同身邊嘅人討論</span></span><br />\n- 多思考，多討論，社會先會進步<br />\n- 帶動返更多人投入運動<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">4) 慎防資訊爆炸</span></span><br />\n- 建議share文宣每日每平台唔好超過3個<br />\n- 文宣之外，社交平台亦要分享返你嘅生活<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">5) Follow 以下page 每日抽少少時間CLS</span></span><br />\n- 香港CLS大軍<br />\n  <a href=\"https://t.me/hkCLSer\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FhkCLSer&d=635WHVioB6XLrmiJ2plDD%2FilxGv0e2UEk%2F7kpEYl8nk%3D&h=52790ce9\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hkCLSer</a><br />\n- 光復YouTube行動頻道<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/OccupyYoutube \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FOccupyYoutube%20&d=635WHVioB6XLrmiJ2plDD%2FilxGv0e2UEk%2F7kpEYl8nk%3D&h=28373e8f\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/OccupyYoutube </a>"},{"pid":"4687005416e1fc32682e22f9d59e08bf8296a32b","tid":1958191,"uid":62799,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T12:33:40.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n手足加油<br />\n特別認同你提到「慎防資訊爆炸」呢一點<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c1d29a4cdd714fcb4d387d8dac8b8fbfe134683","tid":1958191,"uid":353200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T12:43:52.000Z","msg":"麻煩師兄借一借個位<br />\n可唔可以入一入嚟幫幫本土議員撇除選舉不利因素,避免立法會選舉時到時發生優先老人同限制點票人數情況<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1958192\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1958192</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"6748fa24e755ef5a5bf6cc8c14da39f8abd0cc36","tid":1958191,"uid":329034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T12:53:19.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"a5a0de60bb3071d46e630bcbdb2ab9950b30ff5f","tid":1958191,"uid":329034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T12:53:32.000Z","msg":"自推 x2"},{"pid":"4868078f6e25f05662def0cbb0c9ee05592b5bed","tid":1958191,"uid":158100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T12:56:13.000Z","msg":"其實少啲批鬥已經好好多"},{"pid":"fd10a1b4c1e747873e95377447a8e5cbec04d321","tid":1958191,"uid":131933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T13:03:10.000Z","msg":"幫你推一推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"