斗膽提出己見 ，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">係時候將抗爭生活化</span></strong>。<br />\n<br />\n老實講呢句說話聽咗咁耐，究竟即係點呢？<br />\n<br />\n我認為只要每一個人每日抽少少時間出嚟，<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">做最自己最有效率嘅事</span></span>，聚沙成塔就會好有效果。<br />\n咁大家有咩崗位係大家可以參與嘅呢？<br />\n<br />\n而我認為有三大戰線值得注意 - 資訊戰、立法會選舉同經濟戰<br />\n<br />\n資訊戰  簡單來說，即是靠大家對本地文宣創作的支持，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">鼓勵手足繼續創作高質文宣。</span></span><br />\n與此同時，透過吸收更多不同嘅知識，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">去裝備好自己</span></span>，為本來嘅戰役做好準備。<br />\n<br />\n原因：<br />\n- 要保持一定人數創作文宣，繼續推動運動發展。<br />\n- 對家不斷進步緊，我地何以能夠怠慢？<br />\n<br />\n點做？<br />\n <span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">1) CLS (Comment Like Share) </span></span><br />\n- 有好文唔好收收埋埋，比身邊人一齊學嘢，一齊討論<br />\n- 每一次CLS會令文宣比更多人睇到<br />\n- 每一個like 都係文宣創作人繼續努力嘅動力<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">2) 支持原創</span></span><br />\n- 文宣也是藝術創作，尊重文宣創作人<br />\n- 良心做人，勿偷圖<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">3) 多同身邊嘅人討論</span></span><br />\n- 多思考，多討論，社會先會進步<br />\n- 帶動返更多人投入運動<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">4) 慎防資訊爆炸</span></span><br />\n- 建議share文宣每日每平台唔好超過3個<br />\n- 文宣之外，社交平台亦要分享返你嘅生活<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">5) Follow 以下page 每日抽少少時間CLS</span></span><br />\n- 香港CLS大軍<br />\n  <a href=\"https://t.me/hkCLSer\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FhkCLSer&d=635WHVioB6XLrmiJ2plDD%2FilxGv0e2UEk%2F7kpEYl8nk%3D&h=52790ce9\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hkCLSer</a><br />\n- 光復YouTube行動頻道<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/OccupyYoutube \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FOccupyYoutube%20&d=635WHVioB6XLrmiJ2plDD%2FilxGv0e2UEk%2F7kpEYl8nk%3D&h=28373e8f\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/OccupyYoutube </a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T17:38:32.000Z","msg":"新戰略，留意下藍絲啲用字再做文宣<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1958483\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1958483</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"f15f00f6732fb5df40d2d5e99e4331408785d5bb","tid":1958191,"uid":243198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T17:50:41.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"e683537185a4a5f5c2d3448822e641a294bc589e","tid":1958191,"uid":243198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T17:50:57.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"4cef09931ed3534b61b44fabfdeb57ea5ccee779","tid":1958191,"uid":138233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T17:54:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64567fa92e233ac2b18b512f3a500ba36c7020b0","tid":1958191,"uid":335485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d1ed90559db381567ccaec2f7f8fc0ad42088fb4","tid":1958191,"uid":235319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T16:01:26.000Z","msg":"上唔到戰場就去連儂牆<br />\n去唔到連儂牆就做社交文宣<br />\n任何一個地方/方式都可以繼續抗爭!<br />\n香港人反抗!"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T17:57:16.000Z","msg":"So fucking true <br />\n光復香港之路，總有適合你嘅位置同任務"},{"pid":"bc0db2de4123f7624e90e6dc905f76ff107da3fd","tid":1958191,"uid":230942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quot